Create a Vue.js component that acts as a dynamic form generator. The component should be able to take a schema object as a prop, which defines the fields of the form, their types (text, select, switch, button), and any additional properties such as placeholder text, options for select fields, and labels. The form should be reactive and update the state as the user interacts with it. The component should also emit an event with the current state of the form when a submit button is clicked.

The schema object should have the following structure:
